  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/ca59b3e726274f518deae8f099b9af1a.jpg\" style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t《英文天天写》是沪江部落一档写作类节目，其目的在于提升大家的英语写作能力。每期节目主持人都会给出一个话题，积极参加的童鞋还会得到主持人的专业点评哦！想提高英语写作的童鞋千万不要错过哦！<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15011/\" style=\"color: rgb(0,90,148); text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/d5e293c817a6488d819f0c13a95230e1.jpg\" style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left: 0px; line-height: 1.8em; margin-right: 5px;\" /></a>去沪江部落订阅本节目！</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>背景介绍：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t近日，我们迎来了微信5.0的时代。如今，微信也成为了我们生活中的一部分，那么它究竟如何改变我们的生活？让我么一起来探讨一下吧！</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t1. Do you use wechat or not? Share your experience with us.</p>\n<p>\n\t2. How does it influence your life?</p>\n<p>\n\t3. DIY one topic as you like, but remember to stick to the theme of it.O(&cap;_&cap;)O~</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tWhen it comes to wechat, I have a few words with my mum. After her <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/retirement\" target=\"_blank\">retirement</a>, she soon fell in love with wechat! It didn't shocked me until one day I've received adding information from my mum! Then, there have been several slight changes in my life. Before sharing an article or a picture, the first thing I need to do is to think about whether to keep her informed of it. Sometimes, mountains of information was sent to my mobile--you know, one <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/typical\" target=\"_blank\">typical</a> sign of mum, which always surprises me. In one word, thanks to wechat, there's one more bridge between my mum and me.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15011/item/805413/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a><br />\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p540085/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p540085\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p540458/\">双11\"心动拾课\"：精品公开课抢先看</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p540682/\">熊孩子数学连年挂科 考得C后老爸喜极而泣</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p540910/\">外媒看中国：北京高考英语改革</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p539331/\">爱生活爱自己：善待自己的15种方式</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p534308/\">今天下班后就要开始做的15件事</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p103560/\">沪江英语资料下载帮助及沪元知识</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p538037/\">魔鬼口语1000句（82）：他是个帅哥</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p539267/\">艾薇儿携手老公演绎伤感新单</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p540676/\">快乐很简单：会让你很开心的14件事</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p538825/\">42个提升自我的实用技巧（上篇）</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江英语</a>  <a href=\"http://jp.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江日语</a>  <a href=\"http://fr.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江法语</a>  <a href=\"http://kr.hujiang.com\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" 